var ENDZONE_WIDTH = getWidth();
var ENDZONE_HEIGHT = 40;
var YARDLINE_SPACING = 40;
var HASHMARK_WIDTH = 20;
var HASHMARK_SPACING = 8;
var LEFT_HASHMARK_XPOS = 80;
var LEFT_HASHMARK_YPOS = 96;
var RIGHT_HASHMARK_XPOS = getWidth() - 96;
var RIGHT_HASHMARK_YPOS = getWidth() - 80;

var returnMan;
var defender;

var knox;
var marceline;
var paris;
var salisbury;
var schyuler;
var westran;
var scotland;

var RETURN_MAN_WIDTH = 40;
var RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT = 40;

var FALCON_WIDTH = 105;
var FALCON_HEIGHT = 35;

var EAST = 0;
var SOUTH = 1;
var WEST = 2;
var NORTH = 3;

var direction;
var dx = 5;
var dy = 0;

function start(){
    field();

    returnMan = new WebImage("https://www.fayette.k12.mo.us/cms/lib/MO01909881/Centricity/Domain/218/Freddie%20Falcon.jpg");
    returnMan.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    returnMan.setPosition(getWidth()/2 - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH/2, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    returnMan.setColor(Color.green);
    add(returnMan);
    bulldogs();

    keyDownMethod(move);
    setTimer(runner,25);


}

function levelOne(){
    defend();
    defender.move(dx,dy);
    nextLevel();
}

function nextLevel(){
    if(returnMan.getY() < ENDZONE_HEIGHT){
        remove(returnMan);

        returnMan = new WebImage("https://www.fayette.k12.mo.us/cms/lib/MO01909881/Centricity/Domain/218/Freddie%20Falcon.jpg");
        returnMan.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
        returnMan.setPosition(getWidth()/2 - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH/2, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
        returnMan.setColor(Color.green);
        add(returnMan);

        addDefender();

    }
}

function addDefender(){
    add(eagles);
}


function collision(){
    var otherElement = getElementAt(returnMan.getX(), returnMan.getY());
    if(otherElement === defender) {
        direction = SOUTH;
    }
}

function defend(){
    if(defender.getX() + RETURN_MAN_WIDTH > getWidth()){
        dx = -dx;
    }

    // Bounce off left wall
    if(defender.getX() < 0){
        dx = -dx;
    }
}

function bulldogs(){
    defender = new WebImage("http://harrisburg.k12.mo.us/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Harrisburg-Bulldog-Mascot-Colored-300x197.jpg");
    defender.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    defender.setPosition(getWidth()/2 - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH/2, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*3);
    add(defender);
}

function eagles(){
    knox= new WebImage("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    knox.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    knox.setPosition(getWidth()/2 - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH/2, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*5);
    add(knox);
}

function tigers(){
    marceline = new WebImage("http://www.linncountyleader.com/storyimage/MO/20150824/NEWS/150829507/AR/0/Marceline-Tigers-logo.jpg");
    marceline.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    marceline.setPosition(getWidth()/2 - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH/2, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*7);
    add(marceline);

}

function coyotes(){
    paris = new WebImage("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    paris.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    paris.setPosition(getWidth()/2 + RETURN_MAN_WIDTH, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*9);
    add(paris);
}

function panthers(){
    salisbury = new WebImage("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    salisbury.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    salisbury.setPosition(getWidth()/2 - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH/2, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*11);
    add(salisbury);
}

function rams(){
    schyuler = new WebImage("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    schyuler.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    schyuler.setPosition(LEFT_HASHMARK_XPOS-1, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*11);
    add(schyuler);
}

function hornets(){
    westran = new WebImage("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    westran.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    westran.setPosition(RIGHT_HASHMARK_XPOS-1, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*11);
    add(westran);
}

function scotlandTigers(){
    scotland = new WebImage("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    scotland.setSize(RETURN_MAN_WIDTH,RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT);
    scotland.setPosition(getWidth()/2 - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH*2, getHeight()-RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT*9);
    add(scotland);
}

function grid(){
    for(var i = 0; i < 11; i++){
        var yardline = new Line(0, ENDZONE_HEIGHT + i * ENDZONE_HEIGHT, getWidth(), ENDZONE_HEIGHT + i * ENDZONE_HEIGHT);
        yardline.setColor(Color.black);
        add(yardline);
    }

    for(var i = 0; i < 50; i++){
        var hashmark = new Line(LEFT_HASHMARK_XPOS, ENDZONE_HEIGHT + i * HASHMARK_SPACING, LEFT_HASHMARK_YPOS, ENDZONE_HEIGHT + i * HASHMARK_SPACING)
        hashmark.setColor(Color.black);
        add(hashmark);
    }

    for(var i = 0; i < 50; i++){
        var hashmark = new Line(RIGHT_HASHMARK_XPOS, ENDZONE_HEIGHT + i * HASHMARK_SPACING, RIGHT_HASHMARK_YPOS, ENDZONE_HEIGHT + i * HASHMARK_SPACING)
        hashmark.setColor(Color.black);
        add(hashmark);
    }
}

function runner(){
    collision();

    if(direction == WEST){
        if(returnMan.getX() > 0){
            returnMan.move(-5,0);
        }
    }
    if(direction == EAST){
        if(returnMan.getX() < getWidth() - RETURN_MAN_WIDTH){
             returnMan.move(5,0);
        }
    }
    if(direction == NORTH){
        if(returnMan.getY() > 0){
           returnMan.move(0,-5);
        }
    }
    if(direction == SOUTH){
        if(returnMan.getY() < getHeight() - RETURN_MAN_HEIGHT){
            returnMan.move(0,5);
        }
    }
}

function field(){
    var endzone = new Rectangle(ENDZONE_WIDTH, ENDZONE_HEIGHT);
    endzone.setPosition(0,0);
    endzone.setColor(Color.black);
    add(endzone);

    var tdFalcons = new Text("FALCONS" , "30pt Arial");
    tdFalcons.setPosition(FALCON_WIDTH, FALCON_HEIGHT);
    tdFalcons.setColor("#DAA520");
    add(tdFalcons);

    endzone = new Rectangle(ENDZONE_WIDTH, ENDZONE_HEIGHT);
    endzone.setPosition(0, getHeight() - ENDZONE_HEIGHT);
    endzone.setColor(Color.black);
    add(endzone);

    var oppFalcons = new Text("FALCONS", "30pt Arial");
    oppFalcons.setPosition(getWidth() - FALCON_WIDTH, getHeight() - FALCON_HEIGHT);
    oppFalcons.setRotation(180,0);
    oppFalcons.setColor("#DAA520");
    add(oppFalcons);

    grid();
}

function move(e){
    if(e.keyCode == Keyboard.LEFT){
        direction = WEST;
    }
    if(e.keyCode == Keyboard.RIGHT){
        direction = EAST;
    }
    if(e.keyCode == Keyboard.UP){
        direction = NORTH;
    }
    if(e.keyCode == Keyboard.DOWN){
        direction = SOUTH;
    }
}
